      <title>摩根大通称比特币矿工利润指标跌至“近期历史最低”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/bitcoin-miner-profit-measure-fell-to-recent-record-low-jpmorgan-says</link>
